If your asking about how I got the ads working I made the camera a child of a SpringArm node and attached this script to the player's KinematicBody
if Input.is_action_pressed("right_click"):
_spring_arm.translation = translation
_spring_arm.translation.y += camera_height
_spring_arm.spring_length = 2
_spring_arm.translation += Vector3.RIGHT.rotated(Vector3.UP, _spring_arm.rotation.y).normalized()
if Input.is_action_just_released("right_click"):
_spring_arm.spring_length = 4
The full script is too big to post so let me know if you want it and I'll send it in a catbox link.

springArm.translation = lerp(oldTranslationVector3, newTranslationVector3, 0.1)
springArm.spring_length = lerp(yourDefaultValueHere, 4, 0.1)
and when you're done aiming, do it in reverse!
